   <conbody>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">The system specific mimic diagram is used
to indicate the operating status of the system. From the LEDs it is
possible to see the status of breakers<ph platform="PxW" class="- topic/ph ">, the rectifier,
the inverter, the battery and the static switches.</ph>
               <ph platform="WxW" class="- topic/ph ">, the inverter and the static switches.</ph>
               <ph platform="SDC" class="- topic/ph ">, the rectifier and the battery.</ph>
            </p>
            <note class="- topic/note ">Only
the default LED colors are shown. Based on customer requests a LED
might have a different color, but the position and function will be
the same.</note>
            <table class="- topic/table ">
               <tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                  <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="20.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="COLSPEC0" colwidth="40.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="3.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                  <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                     <row valign="bottom" class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry align="left" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Mimic Diagram Symbol</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Symbol Name</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">LED Description
/ Symbol Description</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                     <row valign="top" class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry align="center" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <image href="../Images/OM_PxW_WxW_SDC_Mimic_Diagram_Switch_0000355515.svg"
                                     placement="inline"
                                     class="- topic/image "/>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Breaker</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Green: The breaker is closed</p>
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Red: The breaker is open</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row valign="top" class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry align="center" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                                 <image href="../Images/OM_PxW_WxW_SDC_Mimic_Diagram_Output-Voltage-OK_0000355514.svg"
                                        placement="inline"
                                        class="- topic/image "/>
                              </fig>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Voltage Measuring</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Green: The voltage is available
and within tolerance</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row platform="PxW SDC" valign="top" class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry align="center" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <image href="../Images/OM_PxW_WxW_SDC_Mimic_Diagram_Rectifier_0000355513.svg"
                                  placement="inline"
                                  class="- topic/image "/>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Rectifier</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Green: The rectifier is switched on.</p>
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Yellow: Boost charge <ph platform="SDC" class="- topic/ph ">(or initial charge)</ph> is enabled on the rectifier.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row platform="PxW SDC" valign="top" class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry align="center" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                                 <image href="../Images/OM_PxW_WxW_SDC_Mimic_Diagram_Battery_0000355512.svg"
                                        placement="inline"
                                        class="- topic/image "/>
                              </fig>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Battery</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Green: The battery supply is
active.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row platform="PxW WxW" valign="top" class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry align="center" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <image href="../Images/OM_PxW_WxW_SDC_Mimic_Diagram_Inverter_0000355511.svg"
                                     placement="inline"
                                     class="- topic/image "/>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Inverter</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Green: The inverter is switched on<fn class="- topic/fn "> The inverter is not synchronized unless the yellow LED is also active.</fn>.</p>
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Yellow: The inverter is synchronized to the bypass voltage.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row platform="PxW WxW" valign="top" class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry align="center" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                              <image href="../Images/OM_PxW_WxW_SDC_Mimic_Diagram_Static-Swtich_0000355510.svg"
                                     placement="inline"
                                     class="- topic/image "/>
                           </fig>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Static Switch</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Green: The static switch is active.</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row valign="top" class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry align="center" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                                 <image href="../Images/PxW_WxW_SDC_Mimic_Diagram_Energy-Flow_0000430790.svg"
                                        placement="inline"
                                        class="- topic/image "/>
                              </fig>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Current flow arrow</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Indicates what direction the current
can flow</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row platform="PxW WxW" valign="top" class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry align="center" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                                 <image href="../Images/PxW_WxW_SDC_Mimic_Diagram_Transformer-Stabilizer_0000430787.svg"
                                        placement="inline"
                                        class="- topic/image "/>
                              </fig>
                           </p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Transformer / Stabilizer</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry align="left" valign="middle" class="- topic/entry ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Indicates if there is a bypass transformer or bypass stabilizer</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
         </sectiondiv>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">This is an example of how the
mimic diagram looks when a system is in <ph platform="PxW WxW" class="- topic/ph ">normal
operation</ph>
               <ph platform="SDC" class="- topic/ph ">float charge</ph>:</p>
            <fig platform="PxW" class="- topic/fig ">
               <image href="../Images/PxW_WxW_SDC_Mimic_Diagram_Normal-operation_0000355516.svg"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
            <fig platform="WxW" class="- topic/fig ">
               <image href="../Images/Mimic_Diagram_WxW_Normal-operation_0000479105.svg"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
            <fig platform="SDC" class="- topic/fig ">
               <image href="../Images/Mimic_Diagram_SDC_Normal-operation_0000510867.svg"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
         </sectiondiv>
      </section>
